                "name": "Dust Cloud",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "Three times per day as a move action, a sorico can shake loose a cloud of dust and sand from its coat that fills its space, providing concealment for 1 round. A light wind disperses this cloud immediately. Any creatures sharing a sorico\u2019s space when it uses this ability must succeed at a DC 13 Fortitude save or they become staggered for 1 round as they cough and sneeze. Creatures that don\u2019t breathe are immune to this effect. The save DC is Constitution-based."
